{"tid":168146,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)星河戰隊1-3","createTime":"2017-03-23T10:48:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T15:12:38.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de633fe7ec9c11c6693371293e2e41606753906c","tid":168146,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T10:48:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg04boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=4ccf5699\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 按左下可轉CC台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg04boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=daf01b00\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/df/Starship_Troopers_-_movie_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fdf%2FStarship_Troopers_-_movie_poster.jpg&h=49b846a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事講述在23世紀，人類與外星昆蟲間的星際戰爭。在地球向外星昆蟲宣戰的一年前，Johnny Rico於布宜諾斯艾利斯就讀高中，期間與另一女同學Carmen相戀。在高中畢業後，Johnny的父親希望兒子升讀哈佛大學，但Johnny眼見Carmen投考軍校，為了追求Carmen，Johnny惟有跟從。軍校根據他們的學業成績，Johnny被編往步兵隊，而Carmen則被編入飛行學校。受訓期間，一位名為Dizzy的高中女同學，同為Johnny在校橄欖球隊的戰術教練，對Johnny仰慕多時，也加入了步兵隊。Carmen成績優異..<br />\n<br />\n2.在虫族突襲布宜諾斯艾利斯之後，聯邦軍隊發動反攻，在坦戈約裡擊潰虫族，並在P行星虜獲虫族首領。在此之後，聯邦軍隊乘勝追擊，派大軍殺向虫族隔離區。殘酷的戰鬥沒有止境，機動部隊第6戰隊遭到虫族圍攻，苦盼救援部隊不得，眼看滅亡在即。關鍵時刻，第6戰隊首領夏普德將軍（埃德&middot;勞特Ed Lauter 飾）與幾名士兵吸引虫族，命令霍頓（Jason-Shane Scott 飾）、珊蒂餘下的戰士前往最近的祖魯角哨站避難..<br />\n<br />\n3.一晃十年過去，地球人和虫族的戰爭如火如荼，愈演愈烈。某日，空軍元帥奧瑪&middot;阿諾克（斯蒂芬&middot;霍根Stephen Hogan飾）來地球人的遠方農場羅庫山視察，時任上校的 強尼&middot;瑞哥（加斯帕&middot;範&middot;迪恩Casper Van Dien飾）陪同視察。在此期間，阿諾克的心智被蟲王操控，他切斷了隔離區的電力，使基地完全失去保護。 是夜，虫族對隔離區發動總攻，地球軍雖頑強抵抗，終因寡不敵眾而告敗，基地淪陷。阿諾克則和一干心腹逃離，飛船迫降在OM-1行星。包括負責人斯蓋&middot;馬歇爾 ，飛行員羅拉&middot;貝克等人在內，都被困在星球上無法脫身。主人公約翰尼&middot;瑞科臨危受命，帶領一隊戰士，前往該星球進行營救任務..<br />\n<br />\n7 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"530af1c801ec07396dba0b5fdcfeb33dbb9932d4","tid":168146,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T10:53:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a4297a4fb669f3a29e854e1ccfba2db0319c3d","tid":168146,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T11:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4049ec3849a7dc2152be8b852186d07965f198ed","tid":168146,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T12:01:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c3a10d0949b6f0f43286066b09df54118f9372","tid":168146,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T13:10:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e76a91c7d70cd9c731cadef50e3a5301716122e","tid":168146,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T13:56:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"252ef156b3434b352c98231544c284c71136df77","tid":168146,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T15:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"